## Domain Metadata Shapes

### health
```typescript
{
  name: string           // "Diabetes medicine", "Guitar practice"
  dose?: string          // "500mg", "as prescribed" (medicine only)
  frequency: string      // "3x daily", "daily", "weekly"
  times: string[]        // ["08:00", "13:00", "20:00"]
}
```

### task
```typescript
{
  subdomain: 'errand' | 'work' | 'personal'
  ephemeral: boolean     // true = expires_at should be set
}
```

### learning
```typescript
{
  horizon: 'lifetime' | 'long' | 'short'   // lifetime = no end, long = months-years
  daily_target_mins?: number               // 30 = 30 min/day target
  resource?: string                        // course name, book, teacher
}
```

### idea
```typescript
{
  tag: 'personal' | 'business' | 'product'
  research_ready: boolean   // always false in MVP — flagged for future IdeaBox
  voice_note_url?: string   // Supabase Storage URL if voice note attached
}
```

### note
```typescript
{
  expires_in_hours: 12 | 24 | 48 | 168    // default: 24
}
```

